&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**Applicants must be U.S. Citizens or U.S. Permanent Residents (Green Card holders) to meet customer and regulatory requirements**&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are pioneering modular motion technologies to power the next generation of innovation for Industrial, Aerospace and Defense. If you&#39;re excited about disrupting legacy industries, and passionate about building next generation technology, let&#39;s chat!&lt;/p&gt;
