&lt;li&gt;We are located in beautiful Torrance, CA and just moved into a new large hangar facility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electrical design, product requirements, component selection, analysis, schematic capture, and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
